notes.text: Recommended update for the Azure and AWS SDKs
notes.title: Title of the patch

notes.text:
This update for the SLE Public Cloud module provides the following fixes:

Azure SDK update:
This update for the Azure SDK and CLI adds support for the AHB (Azure Hybrid Benefit).
(bsc#1176784, jsc#ECO-3105)

AWS SDK update:
This update for the AWS SDK updates python-boto3 to version 1.17.9 and aws-cli to 1.19.9.
(bsc#1182421, jsc#ECO-3352)

Security fix for python-urllib3:

- Improve performance of sub-authority splitting in URL. (bsc#1187045, CVE-2021-33503)

notes.text: An issue was discovered in urllib3 before 1.26.5. When provided with a URL containing many @ characters in the authority component, the authority regular expression exhibits catastrophic backtracking, causing a denial of service if a URL were passed as a parameter or redirected to via an HTTP redirect.
